&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-10957&quot; title=&quot;fix potential NPE in SolrCoreParser.init&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-10957&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-10957&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Changed SolrCoreParser.init to use the resource loader from getSchema() instead of the resource loader from getCore().&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
